{"tid":38187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】【暖入心】男童冇錢買日日嚟打機 好心店員送一部畀佢","createTime":"2016-12-13T18:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T08:35:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a17972f83b5ff70b5930fc0e97472fd5ff20323c","tid":38187,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"2016-12-13 20:25:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【更新影片】美國紐約一名男童由於父母無法負擔一部遊戲機，每天都到同一間電子商品店「試玩」遊戲，有職員知道後便送他一部全新遊戲機，讓他提早收到聖誕禮物。<br />\n<br />\n影片是由自稱商店經理的人上載，可見男童當時正在陳列的Wii U遊戲機前「試玩」，一名職員拿着全新的遊戲機走近他，說：「我們買了一部Wii U給你，你不用每天都來玩。」<br />\n<br />\n但男童被大嚇一跳，不敢立即拿取遊戲機，職員再三強調是送給他，又向他展示收據，他才收下，最後職員還送他回家。<br />\n<br />\n商店經理指男童的父母買不起遊戲機，男童想玩於是便天天到來，據悉一部Wii U遊戲機連《Mario Kart》遊戲盛惠300美元（2,340港元）。"},{"pid":"9cc152a086bb2a5b0ba1ee619725c0547301eb51","tid":38187,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161213&amp;guid=56040390&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161213%26guid%3D56040390%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=WDMGX52A1KcV%2Fr3RIxTRRqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=4b7b2adf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161213%26guid%3D56040390%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=ab660dae\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161213&amp;guid=56040390&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"f00e1e7ddd480b154dcca28f7720af98e547387a","tid":38187,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"wii u無人要咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00f6e1e8f183480